And so like that is like a hard thing to sell and like not really our edge in doing. But there are these people who want to do it today. And that's what we're targeting. We're basically showing them, hey, like out of all the DeFi protocols, most of them are not serious. Most of them are just loans of something that like sort of works like a bandaid solution.
